<li><span class="citation Journal">Comrie, Bernard &amp; Polinsky, Maria (1999). "Reflexivity in Tsez". <i>Typology and Linguistic Theory: From Description to Explanation, for the 60th Birthday of Aleksandr E. Kibrik</i>: 319–339.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Reflexivity+in+Tsez&amp;rft.jtitle=Typology+and+Linguistic+Theory%3A+From+Description+to+Explanation%2C+for+the+60th+Birthday+of+Aleksandr+E.+Kibrik&amp;rft.aulast=Comrie%2C+Bernard+%26+Polinsky%2C+Maria&amp;rft.au=Comrie%2C+Bernard+%26+Polinsky%2C+Maria&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.pages=319%E2%80%93339&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Tsez_language"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><span class="citation Journal">Comrie, Bernard &amp; Polinsky, Maria (2003). "Constraints on reflexivization in Tsez". <i>Current Trends in Caucasian, East European and Inner Asian Linguistics: Papers in Honor of Howard I. Aronson</i>: 265–289.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Constraints+on+reflexivization+in+Tsez&amp;rft.jtitle=Current+Trends+in+Caucasian%2C+East+European+and+Inner+Asian+Linguistics%3A+Papers+in+Honor+of+Howard+I.+Aronson&amp;rft.aulast=Comrie%2C+Bernard+%26+Polinsky%2C+Maria&amp;rft.au=Comrie%2C+Bernard+%26+Polinsky%2C+Maria&amp;rft.date=2003&amp;rft.pages=265%E2%80%93289&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Tsez_language"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li>Khalilov, Majid Sh. (1999). <i>Цезско-русский словарь</i> (Tsez-Russian dictionary). Moskva: Academia. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/5874440860" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 5-87444-086-0</a></li>
<li><span class="citation Journal">Polinsky, Maria &amp; Comrie, Bernard (1999). "Agreement in Tsez". <i>Folia Linguistica</i> <b>33.2</b> (Studies in Agreement): 109–130.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Agreement+in+Tsez&amp;rft.jtitle=Folia+Linguistica&amp;rft.aulast=Polinsky%2C+Maria+%26+Comrie%2C+Bernard&amp;rft.au=Polinsky%2C+Maria+%26+Comrie%2C+Bernard&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.volume=33.2&amp;rft.issue=Studies+in+Agreement&amp;rft.pages=109%E2%80%93130&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Tsez_language"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><span class="citation Journal">Polinsky, Maria &amp; Potsdam, Eric (2001). "Long-Distance Agreement and Topic in Tsez". <i><a href="/wiki/Natural_Language_and_Linguistic_Theory" title="Natural Language and Linguistic Theory">Natural Language and Linguistic Theory</a></i> <b>19</b> (19): 583–646. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1023%2FA%3A1010757806504" class="external text" rel="nofollow">10.1023/A:1010757806504</a>.</span><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Long-Distance+Agreement+and+Topic+in+Tsez&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BNatural+Language+and+Linguistic+Theory%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Polinsky%2C+Maria+%26+Potsdam%2C+Eric&amp;rft.au=Polinsky%2C+Maria+%26+Potsdam%2C+Eric&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.volume=19&amp;rft.issue=19&amp;rft.pages=583%E2%80%93646&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1023%2FA%3A1010757806504&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Tsez_language"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
